result.name: 350 Rhode Island St Garage
result.note: Early Bird: $17

reviews.name: Liz G.
reviews.review: I would NOT park in this garage under any circumstances!  It charged me $25 for a mere 8 minutes of parking in its lot, running into the Citibank to hand the teller something, and return to my car.  WHO does that except something looking to rip off people -- in the midst of a pandemic no doubt????????  I complained to the guy on site (have his photo), but he was unprofessional, unsympathetic and very rude. I will NEVER return to this lot, and I will spread the word that no one should patronize this lost.  Horrible.
